            . I am a servant to Mr. Edwards, pawnbroker Clare-market. I have two pair of spoons<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181009190059"></xptr>pledged on the 25th of April, by Wier, six spoons, on the 30th of January, in the name of 
